    stem: 'You trained a model, packaged it with a custom Docker container for serving, and deployed it to Vertex AI Model Registry. When you submit a batch prediction job, it fails with this error: "Error model server never became ready. Please validate that your model file or container configuration are valid." There are no additional errors in the logs. What should you do?',
